# GitHub Actions Automation (`.github/workflows/`)

This project heavily utilizes GitHub Actions for automation. Key workflows include:

*   **Profile Metrics Generation:** `[main.yml](mdc:.github/workflows/main.yml)`
*   **Starred Content Processing:** `[awesome-stars.yml](mdc:.github/workflows/awesome-stars.yml)`
*   **README.md Updates:** `[waka.yml](mdc:.github/workflows/waka.yml)` and `[blog-post-workflow.yml](mdc:.github/workflows/blog-post-workflow.yml)`
*   **Asset Generation Workflows (Currently Broken):** `[qr.yml](mdc:.github/workflows/qr.yml)` and `[wordclouds.yml](mdc:.github/workflows/wordclouds.yml)`
